Evaluation-Only Notice

The materials in this repository are provided for research review, educational discussion, and reproducibility-oriented evaluation.

They are not provided as spacecraft hardware design, thermal-vacuum-validated technology, flight-control software, certified aerospace safety system, or commercial cooling technology.

Any applied, experimental, aerospace, safety-critical, industrial, or spacecraft use requires independent expert review, high-fidelity validation, thermal-vacuum testing, domain-specific safety assessment, and appropriate legal/regulatory review.

